ADR-019 background conversations implemented:
- DB migration v16: processed flag on messages, processing_status on conversations
- ConversationEventBus: per-conversation broadcast channels
- Processor: background task loops on unprocessed messages, broadcasts events
- send_message: fire-and-forget, stores user msg, spawns processor
- GET /conversations/{id}/events: SSE with replay from after_message_id
- Frontend: EventSource subscription, dedup on replay, cleanup on unmount
- Old stream_message kept for backward compat
